CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1962, pg. A14 reads: "The Chi's Have Fun - The tables above represent just a few of 25 hosted by the Chi's at the supper dance last Saturday night. Dr. M.R. Hadley's table is at left.  From left: Dr. and Mrs. Ulysses Williams, Dr. and Mrs. L.R. Downing, Dr. Hadley and guests, Mr. and Mrs. Albert Garland.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Dr. and Mrs. Ulysses Williams, Dr. and Mrs. L.R. Downing, Dr. M.R. Hadley and, Mr. and Mrs. Albert Garland, seated at table in Hilton Hotel for Chi Delta Mu supper dance
